These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, skydiving, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, drama, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, surfing, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, trike, train, subway
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 2. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 3. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 5. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 8. the person watching sports movies is between the person driving the trike and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 9. the person driving the subway is the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
13. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the train##1
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games     | rock-climbing   | baking | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | sports   | superhero   | drama  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | surfing  | swimming  | basketball |
| Transport     | boat    | train | trike     | subway    |

