.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, mirinda, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peach, strawberry, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, hip-hop, jazz
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, goat, lizard
 1. the fan of hip-hop is between the owner of the hedgehog and the fan of country##2
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the fan of country##8
 6. the person eating radish is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of techno is the owner of the snake##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
13. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
14. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
15. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
17. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the fan of country##8
18. the person eating peach is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
19. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | mirinda | iced-tea  | tea  |
| Food          | radish     | peach | avocado | strawberry  |
| Music-Genre   | country    | hip-hop  | jazz | techno |
| Pet           | goat | lizard | hedgehog    | snake  |

