The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, biathlon, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
 7. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
