.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, radish, potato, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, fishing, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, bartender, coach, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, parkour, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the firefighter##6
 2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 3. the person eating pepper is the coach##1
 4. the person eating radish is between the firefighter and the bartender##2
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the project-manager##1
10. the bartender is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person eating pear##8
12. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | potato    | radish             | pear   | pepper     |
| Hobby   | hiking | fishing            | photography | card-games    |
| Job     | bartender | project-manager | firefighter  | coach |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | skateboarding               | parkour  | sailing   |

