 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the turkish##8
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
 8. the japanese is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
10. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
11. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person watching thriller movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
13. the japanese is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
14. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

