.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, fanta, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, accountant, security-guard, fantacher
There are 4 different nationalities: german, malaysian, australian, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, taxi, helicopter, car
 1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 2. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the fantacher##8
 3. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 4. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 5. the person driving the helicopter is the australian##1
 6. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the malaysian##8
 7. the person drinking lemonade is not the colombian##6
 8. the accountant is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking lemonade##7
 9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
10. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the accountant##3
11. the security-guard is on the right of the chef##1
12. the accountant is not the german##6
13. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
15. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the accountant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | cola   | fanta        | milk  |
| Job           | fantacher     | accountant | chef | security-guard  |
| Nationality   | german | colombian    | australian   | malaysian     |
| Transport     | car       | trike     | helicopter    | taxi |

