 4. the indonesian is not the fan of metal##6
 5. the fan of trance is not to the left of the fan of techno##8
 6. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 7. the indonesian is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 8. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
 9. the fan of techno is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of house##7
10. the fan of techno is not to the left of the thai##8
11. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the fan of trance##8
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the fan of trance is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
15. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5

