.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, house, electronic, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, baseball, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, roller, scooter
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of house##8
11. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | tea     | lemonade    | cola |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | disco      | electronic     | house     |
| Sport         | weightlifting | baseball  | badminton     | rugby  |
| Transport     | airplane     | roller | scooter | motorbike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, drawing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, jazz, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, polish, russian, australian
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the australian##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 3. the person drinking 7up is the fan of blues##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the russian##3
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
10. the fan of jazz is not the egyptian##6
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
12. the australian is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
13. the fan of folk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
14. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | 7up  | tea | iced-tea        |
| Hobby         | video-games | filmmaking   | gardening   | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | blues   | jazz    | hip-hop      |
| Nationality   | polish   | australian | russian   | egyptian    |

