.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, mirinda, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, lawyer, engineer
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, lizard, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, motorbike, roller
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 2. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the firefighter##8
 3. the owner of the horse is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 6. the person driving the roller is the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the engineer is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
 8. the lawyer is on the far right##1
 9. the firefighter is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
10. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
12. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
13. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the engineer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | fanta          | soy-milk | mirinda        | cola    |
| Job         | engineer | architect   | firefighter | lawyer  |
| Pet         | lizard           | horse     | frog       | mouse  |
| Transport   | roller            | motorbike   | bike     | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, magic-tricks, video-games, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, software-developer, security-guard, videographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, scooter, boat
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 2. the lawyer is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the ship##1
 4. the lawyer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 5. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 8. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the security-guard##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the videographer##7
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | soy-milk        | hot-chocolate        | tea        | mirinda   |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks      | collecting      | drawing | video-games |
| Job         | videographer | security-guard | software-developer     | lawyer  |
| Transport   | scooter          | car      | ship     | boat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, traveling, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, pilot, lawyer, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, mystery, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, country, dubstep
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the engineer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 4. the musician is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the lawyer##6
 6. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the fan of house##8
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the lawyer##8
 8. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 9. the fan of country is in an even position##4
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
11. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the lawyer and the person who's hobby is reading##2
13. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading    | traveling   | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks |
| Job           | engineer | pilot    | lawyer | musician    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | epic | martial-arts     | disaster    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | country      | house         | dubstep     |

 